### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Root Endpoint
GET http://localhost:3000/

### List Fonts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/fonts

### Generate Simple SVG
POST http://localhost:3000/api/svg
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hello World",
  "options": {
    "fontSize": 72,
    "attributes": {
      "fill": "#333333"
    }
  }
}

### Generate SVG with Custom Anchor
POST http://localhost:3000/api/svg
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Centered Text",
  "options": {
    "fontSize": 48,
    "anchor": "center middle",
    "attributes": {
      "fill": "#ff0000"
    }
  }
}

### Generate Multiline SVG
POST http://localhost:3000/api/svg
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Line 1\\nLine 2\\nLine 3",
  "options": {
    "fontSize": 36,
    "lineHeight": 1.5,
    "textAlign": "center",
    "attributes": {
      "fill": "#0000ff"
    }
  }
}

### Generate SVG with Arc
POST http://localhost:3000/api/svg
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Curved Text",
  "options": {
    "fontSize": 60,
    "envelope": {
      "arc": {
        "angle": 30
      }
    },
    "attributes": {
      "fill": "#00aa00"
    }
  }
}

### Get Path Data Only
POST http://localhost:3000/api/svg/path
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Path Only",
  "options": {
    "fontSize": 48
  }
}

### Get Metrics Only
POST http://localhost:3000/api/svg/metrics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Metrics Test",
  "options": {
    "fontSize": 72
  }
}

### Debug Mode
POST http://localhost:3000/api/svg
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Debug Mode",
  "options": {
    "fontSize": 60
  },
  "debug": true
}

### Get Cache Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cache/stats

### Clear Font Cache
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cache/clear